  "prompt": "My girlfriend has been hinting at us becoming more serious. She's been on vacation for two weeks and hasn't contacted me. Is she testing me?",
  "response": "It's possible that your girlfriend is giving you some space to see how you react, but there could also be many other reasons for her lack of contact. People go on vacation for various reasons, including wanting to disconnect and enjoy their time away. It's important not to jump to conclusions.\n\nIf you feel comfortable, consider reaching out to her to express your feelings and see how she's doing. Open communication can help clarify any misunderstandings and strengthen your relationship. Just keep in mind that a lack of contact during a vacation doesn't necessarily indicate a test; it could simply be that she's enjoying her time away.",
